容是：</h2><p> <strong>NCT梦<br /></strong><strong>NCT的希望<br /></strong><strong>Wayv</strong><br /> <strong>Suho（EXO）<br /></strong> <strong>chanyeol（EXO）</strong> <strong><br />riize</strong></p><h2> SMTown Live 2025在伦敦的详细信息是：</h2><p><strong>日期：</strong> 2025年6月28日<br /><strong>地点：</strong>伦敦，英国，安联体育场Twickenham<br /><strong>门票价格：</strong> TBA<br /><strong>门票销售：</strong> TBA<br /><strong>组织者：</strong>前线</p><figure id="attachment_3836449" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3836449" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3836449" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/SMTOWN-LIVE-in-London-Poster-1st-Lineup.jpg" alt="SMTown Live in London 2025阵容详细信息门票" width="2000" height="2667" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/SMTOWN-LIVE-in-London-Poster-1st-Lineup.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/SMTOWN-LIVE-in-London-Poster-1st-Lineup-400x533.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/SMTOWN-LIVE-in-London-Poster-1st-Lineup-800x1067.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/SMTOWN-LIVE-in-London-Poster-1st-Lineup-696x928.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/SMTOWN-LIVE-in-London-Poster-1st-Lineup-1392x1856.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/SMTOWN-LIVE-in-London-Poster-1st-Lineup-1068x1424.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3836449" class="wp-caption-text"> Smtown Live on London 2025海报。信用：SM娱乐</figcaption></figure><p>伦敦是少数城市SM娱乐公司之一，将与<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/smtown-live-2025-artist-line-up-cities-dates-tickets-more-3818576">墨西哥城，东京和洛杉矶</a>一起参加SMTown Live 2025巡回演出，并宣布更多停留。这次巡回演唱会于1月在首尔的Gocheok Sky Dome举行的两晚音乐会开始，并将于今年5月继续在墨西哥城的第一站。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/smtown-live-2025-london-line-up-tickets-details-more-3836431">伦敦的Smtown Live 2025年现场直播：Riize，NCT Dream，Exo的Suho等人</a>首先出现在<a href